# ``models/`` excludes user-level ML model caches (GGML / ONNX binaries)
# but must NOT swallow source-code directories that happen to be named
# ``models`` — the python-sidecar pydantic schemas live there. The ``*.py``
# unignore is narrow on purpose so runtime caches (__pycache__) and model
# artefacts (*.bin, *.onnx) cannot sneak back in through the exception.
models/
!python-sidecar/app/models/
!python-sidecar/app/models/*.py

.build/
Package.resolved
/package-lock.json
/scripts/package-lock.json

